  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b13f",
      "text": "(Column) Example of \"to write all out\" method",
      "created": 1554533771,
      "updated": 1556688566,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b140",
      "text": "I used the method described in this chapter for years. I use the method for preparing lectures. I also used the method to write this book.",
      "created": 1554533771,
      "updated": 1554533782,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b141",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b142",
      "text": "So, as a concrete example here, I show you some pieces for the chapter.",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b143",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b144",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/e9f5bb041ededf27c04c0a116d4b5f13]",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b145",
      "text": "Fig: the actual pieces for writing this chapter",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b146",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b147",
      "text": "Rough translation of each piece for English readers is as follow. The broken grammar is intentional because I didn't care about grammatical correctness when I made the real Japanese pieces.):",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b148",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b149",
      "text": " Method to organize thought",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b14a",
      "text": " thought won't be organized:",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b14b",
      "text": " \ttoo much?",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533796,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b14c",
      "text": " \ttoo less?",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533796,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b14d",
      "text": " report",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b14e",
      "text": "\t\tcan't write",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533798,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b14f",
      "text": " Do I need to create new knowledge?→(6)",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b150",
      "text": "\t\tBut organizing also build new pyramid in brain",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533807,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b151",
      "text": " Too many tasks, confusing",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b152",
      "text": "  → related to chapter 2",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b153",
      "text": "\t GTD = write out method",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533815,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b154",
      "text": " Too much? Too less?",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b155",
      "text": " Try to write 5 minutes",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b156",
      "text": " First try to write 100 pieces",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b157",
      "text": " write out method",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b158",
      "text": "  First write everything come up with",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533830,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b159",
      "text": " Try to write 100 pieces",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b15a",
      "text": "  measurable goal",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b15b",
      "text": "  interrupt-able",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b15c",
      "text": "  →dupulication is OK",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b15d",
      "text": " level is not aligned first they come out",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b15e",
      "text": " don't mind dupulication, together after",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b15f",
      "text": " can write only less → lack of material to think",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b160",
      "text": "  write out → small number → evidence of lack",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b161",
      "text": "  back to chapter 4 and read 3 books roughly",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b162",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b163",
      "text": "You can see that there are many duplications in the content.",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b164",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533879,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b165",
      "text": "I made pieces once when I planed the contents of this book. It was in May 2016. I wrote \"first try to write 100 pieces\" because I usually do that.",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b166",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b167",
      "text": "After that, I left those pieces for chapter 5 aside and wrote the previous chapters. When I was writing the way to motivate yourself in Chapter 2, I noticed that it is a too big task for readers who are unfamiliar with the \"to write all out\" method. They can not predict how long the task takes. ([(2.3.1) Task is too big])",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533928,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b168",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b169",
      "text": "In Chapter 2 [(2.3.2) Timeboxing],  I explained the method to motivate yourself by making a task smaller, breaking it by time.",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533898,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b16a",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b16b",
      "text": "As a concrete application of [timeboxing], I add a new piece \"try to write 5 minutes\" that keeps the first step small. And then I re-arranged those pieces, and convert them into sentences. It was August 2017.",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533948,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b16c",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554533772,
      "updated": 1554533772,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e0000d0b16d",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1556688566,
